PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776697866
OL,3,CFuneral of Moya Brennan filled with
OL,4,CLoud applause, cheers and standing
OL,5,Covation
OL,7,FTheir distinctive and haunting sound
OL,8,Fhas sold more than 10 million albums
OL,9,Fworldwide and Moya Brennan later had a
OL,10,Fsolo career.
OL,12,FAnother of the Brennan siblings, Enya,
OL,13,Fleft the group in 1981 to embark on a
OL,14,Fhugely successful solo career.
OL,16,FMourners at her funeral included Enya,
OL,17,FU2 members Bono, The Edge, Adam
OL,18,FClayton and Larry Mullen Jr, Daniel
OL,19,FO'Donnell and his wife Majella, and
OL,20,FAndrea Corr.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776697866
OL,3,CFuneral of Moya Brennan filled with
OL,4,CLoud applause, cheers and standing
OL,5,Covation
OL,7,FIreland's President Catherine Connolly
OL,8,Fand Taoiseach Micheal Martin were
OL,9,Frepresented at the service at St
OL,10,FPatrick's Church in Meenaweal, Crolly,
OL,11,Fin the Irish-speaking Gweedore area.
OL,13,FA guard of honour was formed outside
OL,14,Fthe church by local primary school
OL,15,Fpupils, a musical marching band and
OL,16,Fstaff from a community centre.
OL,18,FPeacemakers, a song by Brennan
OL,19,Ffeaturing the voice of her son Paul
OL,20,Fwhen he was four years old, played as
OL,21,Fthe coffin entered the church.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
