FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776697866
OL,3,CFuneral of Moya Brennan filled with
OL,4,CLoud applause, cheers and standing
OL,5,Covation
OL,7,FSome of the symbols of her life
OL,8,Fbrought to the altar included
OL,9,FBrennan's harp, a lanyard from the
OL,10,Flast gig she played, and a Donegal GAA
OL,11,Fjersey.
OL,13,FLater during the service there were
OL,14,Fmusical performances, including by
OL,15,FO'Donnell and Brennan's siblings
OL,16,FCiaran and Pol.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
