PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776697866
OL,3,CFuneral of Moya Brennan filled with
OL,4,CLoud applause, cheers and standing
OL,5,Covation
OL,7,FA recording of Brennan singing Perfect
OL,8,FTime, which she performed in Rome in
OL,9,F2000 in front of Pope John Paul II and
OL,10,Fmore than two million people, was also
OL,11,Fplayed.
OL,13,FParish priest Brian O Fearraig led the
OL,14,Fservice, recalling how on Monday
OL,15,Fnight, it seemed as if a "sacred
OL,16,Fsilence descended for a while" after
OL,17,FBrennan passed.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
